song.title: Dandelion Ride
song.info:
The following songs were tracked with Famitracker (a tracker that emulates the sound of the NES). The expansion chip used is given next to the release date.
Dandilion Ride (VRC6, Jan 2012)
"O'hai.. Famicompo Mini 8 entry. 2nd Place! :D
I've just realised I haven't made an mp3 of this available anywhere yet... better fix that. I guess I should also start uploading my music is more places, especially now that 8bc is dead (temporarily, hopefully)
By the way, I'm fully aware that Dandelion is spelt wrong... unfortunately, I didn't realise this when I submitted the file in the first place, and cba to change it"
